A boilerplate php project with Klein router.

Clone it.
cd into cloned directory and run 'composer install'.
Run 'bower install' to install client side packages such as jquery and bootstrap.
chmod +x dev_server.sh
"./dev_server.sh" to start the development server.
lynx --dump localhost:8080

For live reload support install browser-sync.
Start browser-sync using "./browsersync.sh" in project root.
The url for browser-sync is : http://your_dev_server_ip:3000.

Note that PHP builtin development server treats URIs with dots as real files on disk.
